<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hot-blooded" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hot-blooded,</orth> 1) amorous, lecherous: <cit><quote>the h. gods assist me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 2</bibl></cit>. 2) passionate, rash: <cit><quote>the h. France,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 215</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>hot-bloodied</emph>).
